snippet.title: Streets of Rage 4 Mr. X Nightmare DLC Gameplay  | Summer of Gaming 2021
snippet.description:
Streets of Rage 4 Mr. X Nightmare DLC gameplay trailer shows off some dope beat 'em up combat with new, upcoming playable characters: Shiva, Max, and Estel.
